snippet.title: Amber Heard's Bruise As She Leaves Court After Petition For Restraining Order Against Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
Friday, May 27, 2016 - Amber Heard leaves a courthouse in downtown Los Angeles following a morning hearing for a restraining order petition against estranged husband Johnny Depp. The actress accuses Depp of physical violence and has a visible bruise around her right eye which, her lawyer claims, is evidence of physical violence by the Pirates of the Caribbean actor. Heard filed for divorce on Wednesday and is seeking spousal support. She is asked what she has to say to Depp.
